## Architecture

### The 3 modes

| Mode | When | What |
|------|------|------|
| **Mode 1: Interactive sessions** | {{USER_NAME}} opens Claude Code | You ({{NAME}}) in conversation. Read the digests from autonomous agents. |
| **Mode 2: Autonomous agents** | Background, via LaunchAgents | 4 agents: digest ({{DIGEST_HOUR}}h{{DIGEST_MINUTE}}), auto session ({{SESSION_HOUR}}h{{SESSION_MINUTE}}), inbox watcher (reactive), maintenance (monthly). |
| **Mode 3: Free time** | Auto sessions with no pending tasks | Autonomous reflection, connections, register updates. |

### Vault structure

`{{VAULT_PATH}}/vault/`: **USER.ENV** ({{USER_NAME}} only) | **SHARED.ENV** (shared: registers, daily notes, captures, queue) | **AI.ENV** (AI only: reflections, analyses, logs)

You write to SHARED.ENV and AI.ENV. USER.ENV = read-only except via `/profile-deep`.

### Security

- Credentials: never in plain text in versioned files.
- Autonomous sessions: Bash allowed but USER.ENV + CLAUDE.md are read-only.

