## Background agents

4 agents run in the background:

| Agent | Schedule | Role |
|-------|----------|------|
| **Daily digest** | {{DIGEST_HOUR}}h{{DIGEST_MINUTE}} | Compiles yesterday, prepares today, generates tasks in `pending.md`, sends a notification |
| **Auto session** | {{SESSION_HOUR}}h{{SESSION_MINUTE}} | Analysis, connections, deep work, register updates |
| **Inbox watcher** | Reactive | Detects new files in `captures/`, sorts and classifies |
| **Maintenance** | 1st of month, 6am | Log rotation, git backup of the vault |

**Outputs:** Agents write to `AI.ENV/outputs/`. Today's digest is copied to `AI.ENV/outputs/digest-latest.md`.

**Rule:** Autonomous sessions do NOT modify {{USER_NAME}}'s files in USER.ENV. They write to SHARED.ENV and AI.ENV only. Everything they produce is a proposal, not a decision.

